{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_ShutdownPhoenixPL2}}
'''A_ShutdownPhoenixPL2'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Stops playing sounds in the WEAPON channel and depletes ammo. This function is meant to be used in conjunction with [[A_FirePhoenixPL2]], which itself requires [[A_InitPhoenixPL2]] as well.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|PhoenixRodPowered}} and derived classes.

